{"id":932,"date":"2019-09-09T19:18:15","date_gmt":"2019-09-09T16:18:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/dev.atomicwallet.io\/?p=932"},"modified":"2020-06-25T20:43:19","modified_gmt":"2020-06-25T17:43:19","slug":"july-report","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/news\/july-report","title":{"rendered":"Atomic Wallet: July Report"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Fusion AMA\"  class=\"wp-image-13463 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_wallet_report-1920x1080.png\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"what-is-done\">What is done:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><a href=\"#desktop\">New Desktop Releases (2.2.0 &#8211; 2.5.1)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#mobile\">Mobile App \u2013 New 0.42.0 Release<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#membership\">Membership Program<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#listing\">Listing Campaign<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#trading\">AWC Trading Competition &#8211; final results<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#ama\">AMAs: Raven Protocol, LTO Network, Thorchain, Fusion, Loopring, Cubiex<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#support\">Support Work in July<\/a><\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"desktop\"><span id=\"desktop-releases-2-2-0-8211-2-5-1\">Desktop Releases (2.2.0 &#8211; 2.5.1)<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/downloads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"1636\"  height=\"1220\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13475 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/auto_update_atomic_wallet.gif\" ><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We manage to update Atomic Wallet desktop version several times this month. What\u2019s new:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Exchange History Tab.<\/li><li>Purchase of AWC and BNB via wallet\u2019s interface<\/li><li>QR-codes with private keys\/mnemonic seed.<\/li><li>Auto-update.<\/li><li>Support for YCash-ZCash fork, Tron-USDT.<\/li><li>Added Wink\/TRC20 token.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You can download Atomic&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/downloads\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"mobile\"><span id=\"mobile-app-new-0-42-0\">Mobile App \u2013 New 0.42.0<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/play.google.com\/store\/apps\/details?id=io.atomicwallet&amp;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"720\"  height=\"405\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13487 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 910w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 720w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 1920w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_mobile_release.png 380w\" ><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In this update we made some improvements. What\u2019s new:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>BNB-BEP2 tokens from Binance DEX added.<\/li><li>Optimisation for low-performance devices.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Get the new mobile version on&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/play.google.com\/store\/apps\/details?id=io.atomicwallet&amp;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Google Play<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"membership\"><span id=\"membership-program\">Membership Program<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/membership\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13499 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-cashback-1920x1080.png\" ><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Atomic is the first cryptocurrency wallet started a multi-level&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/membership\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">membership program<\/a>, based on its native Atomic Wallet Token. AWC-BEP2 holders will receive a monthly cash back for using a built-in exchange service. By the end of July, 50 users have already joined the program and received their first rewards. Membership program is available for everyone, tokens are rewarded for every exchange.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"support-work-in-july\">Support Work in July<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/support.atomicwallet.io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"1920\"  height=\"1080\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13511 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/support_service_atomic_wallet-1920x1080.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/support_service_atomic_wallet.png 1920w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/support_service_atomic_wallet-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/support_service_atomic_wallet-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/support_service_atomic_wallet-1536x864.png 1536w\" ><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This month, our support team reacted on 2518 issues in less than 1 hour. In case of any problem, reach us by email or live chat widget on our website. Atomic support service works for you 24\/7.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"listing\"><span id=\"listing-campaign\">Listing Campaign<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/voting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13523 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/voting_campaign-1920x1080.png\" ><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We support all ERC20 &amp; BEP2 tokens. However, getting a lot of requests for listing everyday, we decided to give our community a choice. Just&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/voting\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">apply and vote<\/a>&nbsp;for your favorite asset to be listed in Atomic Wallet with a pretty icon.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"trading\"><span id=\"awc-trading-competition\">AWC Trading Competition<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/token\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"1234\"  height=\"912\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13535 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 1234px) 100vw, 1234px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 273w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 693w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 1461w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/awc_trading_competition.png 1234w\" ><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We held AWC token trading competition on Binance Dex this month. Over 2000 people traded with us. By the end of 35 days, participants have made $20,000,000+ volume and distributed $80,000 rewards. You\u2019re welcome to see&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/spreadsheets\/d\/1rAhSV7Qf_R9bVVjHiT9PmLIJzIxxecwY7F68qU0y4KY\/edit#gid=932694704\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">the leaderboard<\/a>&nbsp;and read about our native&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/token\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">token AWC<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"ama\"><span id=\"amas-in-july\">AMAs in July<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"720\"  height=\"405\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13547 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_wallet_ama_session.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_wallet_ama_session.png 720w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic_wallet_ama_session-300x169.png 300w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We made a few AMA sessions in our&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/t.me\/atomicwalletchat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Telegram chat<\/a>&nbsp;this month. Our community was introduced to these projects: Raven Protocol, LTO Network, Thorchain and Fusion Foundation. You\u2019re welcome to read our digests:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/medium.com\/@atomicwallet\/ama-session-with-raven-protocol-essential-points-28f9aa81aab2\" target=\"_blank\">Raven Protocol<\/a><\/li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/steemit.com\/cryptocurrency\/@atomicwallet\/ama-session-with-lto-network-essential-points\" target=\"_blank\">LTO Network<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/thorchain-ama\">Thorchain<\/a><\/li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/fusion-ama\" target=\"_blank\">Fusion Foundation<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019re happy to work on Atomic Wallet for you! Be always aware of our news and updates with&nbsp;<a hre